template(name="App_intro")
  #introPage.extraPage
    .intro-wrap
        .intro-description
            h1 BulletNotes.io
            h2 Organize your life
            if currentUser
              a.register.mdl-button--raised.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored(href='/') Your Notes
            else
              a.register.mdl-button--raised.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored(href='/join') Create Free Account
              a.signIn.mdl-button--raised.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored(href='/signin') Sign in
            a.signIn.mdl-button--raised.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored(href='https://telegram.me/bulletnotesbot',target='_blank') Get started on Telegram

        .intro-media
          .shot.shot1
            .shot-i(style="background-image: url('/img/intro/intro1.png')")
          .shot.shot2
            .shot-i(style="background-image: url('/img/intro/intro2.png')")
          .shot.shot3
            .shot-i(style="background-image: url('/img/intro/intro3.png')")


    .mdl-grid
      .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col
        .icon-block
          h2
            i.material-icons flash_on
          h5 Fast note entry
          p Enter notes multiple ways, from telling Siri to remind you of something, to sending a text, email or Telegram chat. Get all your thoughts in one place and sort it out later.
      .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col
        .icon-block
          h2.center.light-blue-text
            i.material-icons group
          h5.center Work Together
          p.light
            | Share a list of notes with someone to collaborate with them. Share a grocery list with your spouse, meeting notes with work colleagues, or your new screenplay with an editor.
      .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col
        .icon-block
          h2.center.light-blue-text
            i.material-icons settings
          h5.center Powerful
          p.light
            | Three different views into your notes gives you ultimate flexibility. The Bullet Notes view is simple and intuitive. The Kanban view is a classic way to get things done. The Calendar view lets you schedule and archive things.

    h2 Save and organize anything with a powerful interface
    ul
        li.mdl-button--raised.mdl-button Todos
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Notes
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Journal Entries
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Writing
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Recipes
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Trip Planning
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Reference
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Study Guides
    h2 Integrations
    h3 Automatically save and categorize information from almost anywhere with our integrations
    ul
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised IFTTT
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Telegram
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised CLI
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised API
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Alfred
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Dropbox
    h2 BulletNotes Pro
    h3 Go Pro and get a slew of extra features
    ul
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Unlimited Notes
        li.mdl-button.mdl-button--raised Nightly Dropbox Backup
    a.register.mdl-button--raised.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored(href='/join') Create Free Account